<h2>&#x221a;bhiṣaj<i> 'heal'</i></h2><p>
<i>present: </i>[2.] <b>bhiṣakti</b> &#xa0; -- <b>abhiṣṇak</b> &#xa0;</p><p>
<i>derivatives: </i><b>bhiṣáj</b> <sub>V.+ </sub>&#xa0;<b>bheṣajá</b> <sub>V.+ </sub>&#xa0;</p><p>
The use of <b>bhiṣaj</b> as a verbal root in RV. is very abnormal.  The denominative <b>bhiṣajyáti</b> etc. V.B., from the noun <b>bhiṣáj</b>, is quite common.</p></body>
